 Jidenna that oyinbo boy from Enugu releases the official music video for “Worth The Weight” featuring Seun Kuti. The Nigerian-American rapper unlocks a new visual for the track ”Worth The Weight” a song off his newly released 11 track album “85 to Africa“. This record is a wake up call for Africans to rediscover themselves and create an highway that will connect the diaspora with the Motherland, then share a common goal. Jidenna teams up with Fela’s son and leader of his band, Seun Kuti for this thoughtful jam. Watch, listen and Enjoy!   The post [Video] Jidenna – “Worth The Weight” ft. Seun Kuti  Source: TooXclusiv